<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="c31May1927"><font color="red">31 May 1927</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver):   But then I never read Rabelais either though nobody will believe this. I will read them both when I get back. I read a few chapters of a book called <i>La langue de Rabelais</i>. I have little inclination at present either to read or write &hellip; Mr Lindbergh, a Norwegian Swedoyank, has arrived in Paris &hellip; Do you think the man or clergyman who wrote that pamphlet might be interested to see t.1? </div>
